**jscan**

`jscan` is a command-line utility to aid in scanning documents to pdf. It has
various options for auto-rotation, clipping, OCR (using Tesseract), and PDF
conversion. It relies in the ImageMagick library for image conversions, the
Tesseract library for OCR, and various Perl modules.

This README is a placeholder and will be replaced with more detailed
information when the project documentation is updated.

This project is considered to be in the alpha development stage.
